reviewText: They ask for projects without building up to it, there's no room for a step-by-step exercises. Theoretically I'm no six sigma expert and that's why I'm here. The same thing was with the other BELTS specialization. So, when do they teach anything or give anything to practice? Never. So disappointed in this course.
Well structures but examples are not clear.
Excellent learning tools and methodology for grow up knowledge and which are applicable for professional life.
